          "Key Messages": ["Multi-Sport Platform", "Vision AI Technology", "Real-time Processing"],
          "Usage Count": 8,
          "Performance Rating": 4,
          "Created By": "Austin Humphrey",
          "Tags": ["High Priority"]
        },
        {
          "Content Title": "Vision AI Technical Specifications",
